# Rublyovka, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Rublyovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Bik-Karmalinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 112 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Rublyovka is located 16 km east of Davlekanovo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Almetovo is the nearest rural locality.
